    "note": "In the error state the radio circle stroke and value text keep their default colors; only the container border, container fill, and selected radio fill turn red. Radio's unselected error border is red-400 #eb4e33 (checkbox uses red-500 #e62200 for the same state) \u2014 this difference is intentional per the design system site."
  }
}